---```
---tex.print(<string> s, ...)
---tex.print(<number> n, <string> s, ...)
---tex.print(<table> t)
---tex.print(<number> n, <table> t)
---```
---
---The very last string of the very last `tex.print` command in a `directlua` will not have the `endlinechar` appended, all others do.
